            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Lari Libero A<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan></supplied> sacr<supplied reason="lost">um</supplied> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Quadratius <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>Quir</abbr><ex>ina</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Quintulus aedilic<supplied reason="lost">iae</supplied> potest<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>tis statuam cum aed<supplied reason="lost">ic</supplied>ula et <lb n="5"/>columnis quam in praefectura <lb n="6"/>sua pro IIIviris agens sponte pol<lb break="no" n="7"/>licitus est praeter leg<supplied reason="lost">iti</supplied>ma HS <lb n="8"/>XX <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ummum</ex></expan> decurionatus re<supplied reason="lost">i <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublicae</ex></expan></supplied> inlata <lb n="9"/>dedit dedicavit<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ocus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Tafel ist in 2 Teile gebrochen. (B): CIL VIII 10867: Z. 1: [P]a[t]ri; Z. 6/7: pol/[l]icitus; Z. 10: l(ocus) d(atus) [d(ecreto) d(ecurionum). Datierung: Die Gottheit ist besonders mit Septimius Severus verbunden (vgl. AE 1942/43, 2 = !953, 185 = 1954, 201e = 1952, p. 52 s. n. 164 = IRT 295).</p>
            </div>
